data.description: Welcome your new oasis. This house features new exterior paint, modern kitchen appliances with ample cabinet space, large living area, a very large Primary bedroom and 2 other bedrooms, plus an additional non conforming bedroom that is already set up with plumbing for washer and dryer or a second bathroom. You could even set it up as a 4th bedroom or office. Did I mention the attached 1 car garage and only 4 blocks from Paradise Valley Elementary School. Call Tony Duncan 307-441-1382 for your showing.
